            "date": "2011-11-08 11:38:32", 
            "sentences": [
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "We need to push the latest code updates for QMO from git (https://github.com/mozilla/quality.mozilla.org) to production at your earliest convenience. ", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": true
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "Sorry for the short notice but today would be great. ", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "If you're all booked solid for today already, let us know your next open launch window (Thursday maybe?)\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": true
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "Note this also adds a languages folder in qmo_content (moving the custom language files out of their plugin folders so they're less likely to be lost in future updates). ", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": true
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "We're also removing some plugins we're no longer using.\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "This upgrade includes a significant version update to Buddypress which is a somewhat delicate process, and just pushing the code without a few added precautions can cause major breakages. ", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": true
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "So the steps will be:\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "1. Deactivate ALL plugins\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "2. Push the code from Git\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "3. Activate ONLY Buddypress and complete its update procedure (creating some new pages, etc)\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "4. Activate the other plugins\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "If we can set up a time for this push I can be online to handle the deactivating/reactivating on the WordPress side of things, we'll just need someone from IT to handle the push from Git.\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": true
                }
            ], 
